# Coding Standards – Image Gallery

**Apply on every task.** Full details in `docs/CODING_STANDARDS.md`

## Section index (read only relevant sections)

§1 Core | §2 React/Next.js | §3 TypeScript | §4 Folder | §5 Performance | §6 Animation | §8 SEO/a11y | §10 Lint | §11 Error | §13 Testing | §14 Copy | §17 SonarQube | §18 Checklist

## Mandatory

- No hardcoding (copy, colors, magic values)
- Tailwind only, no inline styles
- Next.js Image for images
- No `any`, define interfaces
- ESLint + Prettier pass
- Files under 300 lines

## Structure

- `src/app/` – pages
- `src/components/` – shared
- `src/lib/` – utils, hooks, constants
- `__tests__/` – tests
